{"title":"Quicksilver Bolt","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Quicksilver_Bolt","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.30](/0.30 \"0.30\")**: This article **may not be** up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of Crawl.*\n\n|   |                                                                                                          |\n| - | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|   | Breathes a bolt of dispelling energy at a targeted creature, possibly removing some of its enchantments. |\n\n**Quicksilver Bolt** is a monster-only spell which fires a blast of irresistible, piercing, magic-dispelling energy. Any target struck by it will take significant damage and have the duration of their magical enhancements drastically reduced. See [list of dispellable effects](/List_of_dispellable_effects \"List of dispellable effects\") for the full list.\n\nThe following enemies cast Quicksilver Bolt:\n\n- d [![Purple draconian.png](/images/7/74/Purple_draconian.png)](/File:Purple_draconian.png) **[Purple draconian](/Purple_draconian \"Purple draconian\")** (3d20 damage)\n- D [![Quicksilver dragon.png](/images/0/04/Quicksilver_dragon.png)](/File:Quicksilver_dragon.png) **[Quicksilver dragon](/Quicksilver_dragon \"Quicksilver dragon\")** (3d20 damage)\n- E [![Quicksilver elemental.png](/images/d/d9/Quicksilver_elemental.png)](/File:Quicksilver_elemental.png) **[Quicksilver elemental](/Quicksilver_elemental \"Quicksilver elemental\")** (3d20 damage)\n- D [![Serpent of Hell (Dis).png](/images/a/a2/Serpent_of_Hell_%28Dis%29.png)](/File:Serpent_of_Hell_\\(Dis\\).png) **[Serpent of Hell (Dis)](/Serpent_of_Hell_\\(Dis\\) \"Serpent of Hell (Dis)\")** (3d21 damage)\n\nThe following enemies may be able to cast Quicksilver Bolt, depending on their spell set:\n\n- & [![Pandemonium lord.png](/images/c/c6/Pandemonium_lord.png)](/File:Pandemonium_lord.png) **[Pandemonium lord](/Pandemonium_lord \"Pandemonium lord\")** (5.2% chance)\n- d [![Tiamat.png](/images/9/9a/Tiamat.png)](/File:Tiamat.png) **[Tiamat](/Tiamat \"Tiamat\")** (3d20 damage, 16.7% chance)\n\nPlayers can duplicate the effect with a [wand of quicksilver](/Wand_of_quicksilver \"Wand of quicksilver\").\n\n## History\n\n- In [0.29](/0.29 \"0.29\"), the [wand of quicksilver](/Wand_of_quicksilver \"Wand of quicksilver\") was introduced, allowing players (and more monsters) access to this spell.\n- Prior to [0.19](/0.19 \"0.19\"), quicksilver bolts did not pierce through enemies.\n- Prior to [0.18](/0.18 \"0.18\"), the spell could occasionally be cast by the player through the use of a [Random Bolt](/Random_Bolt \"Random Bolt\") spell, as evoked through a [rod of destruction](/Rod_of_destruction \"Rod of destruction\").\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Quicksilver Bolt - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Quicksilver_Bolt\",\"wgTitle\":\"Quicksilver Bolt\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":73226,\"wgRevisionId\":73226,\"wgArticleId\":6982,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"0.30 articles\",\"Monster spells\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"