t-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #f90; background-color: #fc6; border-left: 15px solid #f90; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Version <a href=\"/0.30\" title=\"0.30\">0.30</a></b>: This article <b>may not be</b> up to date for the <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">latest stable release</a> of Crawl.</i></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> Breathes a bolt of dispelling energy at a targeted creature, possibly removing some of its enchantments.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><b>Quicksilver Bolt</b> is a monster-only spell which fires a blast of irresistible, piercing, magic-dispelling energy. Any target struck by it will take significant damage and have the duration of their magical enhancements drastically reduced. See <a href=\"/List_of_dispellable_effects\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"List of dispellable effects\">list of dispellable effects</a> for the full list.\n</p><p>The following enemies cast Quicksilver Bolt:\n</p>\n<ul><li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-magenta\">d</span> <a href=\"/File:Purple_draconian.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Purple draconian.png\" src=\"/images/7/74/Purple_draconian.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Purple_draconian\" title=\"Purple draconian\">Purple draconian</a></b> (3d20 damage)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-brightcyan\">D</span> <a href=\"/File:Quicksilver_dragon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Quicksilver dragon.png\" src=\"/images/0/04/Quicksilver_dragon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Quicksilver_dragon\" title=\"Quicksilver dragon\">Quicksilver dragon</a></b> (3d20 damage)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-brightcyan\">E</span> <a href=\"/File:Quicksilver_elemental.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Quicksilver elemental.png\" src=\"/images/d/d9/Quicksilver_elemental.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Quicksilver_elemental\" title=\"Quicksilver elemental\">Quicksilver elemental</a></b> (3d20 damage)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-lightgray\">D</span> <a href=\"/File:Serpent_of_Hell_(Dis).png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Serpent of Hell (Dis).png\" src=\"/images/a/a2/Serpent_of_Hell_%28Dis%29.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"48\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Serpent_of_Hell_(Dis)\" title=\"Serpent of Hell (Dis)\">Serpent of Hell (Dis)</a></b> (3d21 damage)</li></ul>\n<p>The following enemies may be able to cast Quicksilver Bolt, depending on their spell set:\n</p>\n<ul><li> <span class=\"nhsym\" style=\"color: #A4C592; border: 1px solid #A4C592;\">&amp;</span> <a href=\"/File:Pandemonium_lord.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Pandemonium lord.png\" src=\"/images/c/c6/Pandemonium_lord.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"48\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Pandemonium_lord\" title=\"Pandemonium lord\">Pandemonium lord</a></b> (5.2% chance)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym\" style=\"color: #A4C592; border: 1px solid #A4C592;\">d</span> <a href=\"/File:Tiamat.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Tiamat.png\" src=\"/images/9/9a/Tiamat.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"48\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Tiamat\" title=\"Tiamat\">Tiamat</a></b> (3d20 damage, 16.7% chance)</li></ul>\n<p>Players can duplicate the effect with a <a href=\"/Wand_of_quicksilver\" title=\"Wand of quicksilver\">wand of quicksilver</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>In <a href=\"/0.29\" title=\"0.29\">0.29</a>, the <a href=\"/Wand_of_quicksilver\" title=\"Wand of quicksilver\">wand of quicksilver</a> was introduced, allowing players (and more monsters) access to this spell.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.19\" title=\"0.19\">0.19</a>, quicksilver bolts did not pierce through enemies.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.18\" title=\"0.18\">0.18</a>, the spell could occasionally be cast by the player through the use of a <a href=\"/Random_Bolt\" title=\"Random Bolt\">Random Bolt</a> spell, as evoked through a <a href=\"/Rod_of_destruction\" title=\"Rod of destruction\">rod of destruction</a>.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240915233512\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.080 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.144 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 112/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 237/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3801/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 505/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 4/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nLua time usage: 0.050s\nLua virtual size: 14.14 MB / 50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  115.228      1 -total\n 67.25%   77.496      1 Template:Monsters_with_spell\n 31.32%   36.094      1 Template:Version030\n 29.97%   34.536      1 Template:Version\n 12.80%   14.746      6 Template:Glyph\n  1.11%    1.279      1 Template:Flavour\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key crawl_wiki-crawl_:pcache:idhash:6982-0!canonical and timestamp 20240915233512 and revision id 73226\n -->\n</div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Quicksilver_Bolt&amp;oldid=73226\">http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Quicksilver_Bolt&amp;oldid=73226</a>\"\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"catlinks\" class=\"catlinks\" data-mw=\"interface\"><div id=\"mw-normal-catlinks\" class=\"mw-normal-catlinks\"><a href=\"/Special:Categories\" title=\"Special:Categories\">Categories</a>: <ul><li><a href=\"/Category:0.30_articles\" title=\"Category:0.30 articles\">0.30 articles</a></li><li><a href=\"/Category:Monster_spells\" title=\"Category:Monster spells\">Mons