desize\":{\"value\":3801,\"limit\":2097152},\"templateargumentsize\":{\"value\":505,\"limit\":2097152},\"expansiondepth\":{\"value\":4,\"limit\":40},\"expensivefunctioncount\":{\"value\":0,\"limit\":100},\"timingprofile\":[\"100.00%  115.228      1 -total\",\" 67.25%   77.496      1 Template:Monsters_with_spell\",\" 31.32%   36.094      1 Template:Version030\",\" 29.97%   34.536      1 Template:Version\",\" 12.80%   14.746      6 Template:Glyph\",\"  1.11%    1.279      1 Template:Flavour\"]},\"cachereport\":{\"timestamp\":\"20240915233512\",\"ttl\":86400,\"transientcontent\":false}}});});</script><script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgBackendResponseTime\":280});});</script>\n\t</body>\n</html>\n","rawPage":"{{version030}}\n{{flavour|Breathes a bolt of dispelling energy at a targeted creature, possibly removing some of its enchantments.}}\n\n'''Quicksilver Bolt''' is a monster-only spell which fires a blast of irresistible, piercing, magic-dispelling energy. Any target struck by it will take significant damage and have the duration of their magical enhancements drastically reduced. See [[list of dispellable effects]] for the full list.\n\n{{monsters with spell}}\n\nPlayers can duplicate the effect with a [[wand of quicksilver]].\n\n==History==\n*In [[0.29]], the [[wand of quicksilver]] was introduced, allowing players (and more monsters) access to this spell.\n*Prior to [[0.19]], quicksilver bolts did not pierce through enemies.\n*Prior to [[0.18]], the spell could occasionally be cast by the player through the use of a [[Random Bolt]] spell, as evoked through a [[rod of destruction]].\n\n[[Category:Monster spells]]"}